  %% Salesforce Opportunity Lifecycle Template
  %% Customize stage names and transitions based on your org

  direction LR

  [*] --> Prospecting

  Prospecting : New opportunity identified
  Prospecting --> Qualification : Meets criteria

  Qualification : Assessing fit and needs
  Qualification --> NeedsAnalysis : Qualified
  Qualification --> ClosedLost : Not qualified

  NeedsAnalysis : Solution discovery
  NeedsAnalysis --> ValueProposition : Requirements defined
  NeedsAnalysis --> ClosedLost : Requirements don't match

  ValueProposition : Presenting solution
  ValueProposition --> ProposalPricingQuote : Interest confirmed
  ValueProposition --> ClosedLost : No interest

  ProposalPricingQuote : Quote generation
  ProposalPricingQuote --> Negotiation : Quote submitted
  ProposalPricingQuote --> ClosedLost : Budget issues

  Negotiation : Terms discussion
  Negotiation --> ClosedWon : Agreement reached
  Negotiation --> ClosedLost : Cannot agree

  ClosedWon : Deal successful
  ClosedWon --> [*]

  ClosedLost : Deal lost
  ClosedLost --> [*]
